    <description><![CDATA[<br/><b>Survival</b> is my first Gamebook-Style text adventure. It is not the best, so it will be revised over time. In this adventure you fight for your survival against a massive zombie horde. Sequels will arrive as soon as they are completed.<br/><br/>One day you wake to a sound of moaning. You look outside your bedroom window. "Zombies!" you exclaim. As the result of the horrific faliure of an experiment to bring deceased people back to life with the chemical Necro, a zombie apocalypse has started. The chemical Necro was partially complete, therefore having partial affect. One day, an explosion at a nearby chemical plant also gouged a hole in the Necro storage tanks which dumped thousands of gallons of the highly toxic chemical Necro into the environment. The chemicals also gave Necro an acidic quality. For some unknown reason, an infected person can produce Necro as an equivalent to their saliva, making spit and bites fatal. The Necro actually did ressurect people, but did not reverse the rotting of corpses and caused them to zombify. Most of the known population was infected. But not you.You run downstairs and find your parents dead. You run out onto the deserted streets to your middle school, only to find it abandoned. Despite that, you run inside. What will you do? <br/><br/>-Page 1, <b>Survival</b><br/><br/>]]></description>
    <author>Padraig MacGabann</author>
    <category>Horror</category>
  </game>
  <object name="Page1">
    <description><![CDATA[You woke today to a sound of moaning. You looked outside your bedroom window. "Zombies!" you exclaimed. As the result of the horrific faliure of an experiment to bring deceased people back to life with the chemical Necro. The chemical Necro was partially complete, therefore having partial affect. One day, an explosion at a nearby chemical plant also gouged a hole in the Necro storage tanks which dumped thousands of gallons of the highly toxic chemical Necro into the environment. The chemicals also gave Necro an acidic quality. For some unknown reason, an infected person can produce Necro as an equivalent to their saliva, making spit and bites fatal. The Necro actually did ressurect people, but did not reverse the rotting of corpses and caused them to zombify. Most of the known population was infected. But not you.You run downstairs and find your parents dead. You run out onto the deserted streets to your middle school, only to find it abandoned. Despite that, you run inside. What will you do?<br/><br/>]]></description>
